<br>
imo, the best instant clicky should be:<br>
<br>
- don't need to equip<br>
- can be use indoor &amp; outdoor<br>
- do not need to target self first<br>
- dont have annoying spell effect(telescope)<br>
<br>
I have a instant clicky ring from doing the PoD quest, it has all the good things i listed except it's kindda annoying that i have to target myself first,... still it's good that i can use it indoor. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wiggletoes>wiggletoes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/19/03 2:15 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Instant click items</span><hr size=1> Sage legs are the best insta-click I have seen.  Good legs and good buff.  Elemental armor.  This stacks with Circle of season from a druid.  Just put EA in top slot with 3 other fakes then few other good but not so needed buffs then kei and virtue or mark of kazad and bot9.  After the druids have cast grp or mgb protection of the seasons click it off re do element armor and have them lay cos on you.  Make sure the druid will do CoS on you before you take PoS off.  <br>
<br>
Some druids get all pizzy about casting this lesser buff on you after having done PoS to the grp.  Just explain that yours stack to make more with CoS and most will do it.  BTW elemental cloak will stack with CoS also.  At the start I use that and follow with the insta-armor after the dispell hits.<br>
<br>
The thurg and SS boots buff stacks with this also but it has to be targeted and takes 3 seconds to do.  Good for getting that FR over 300 buffed with no bard. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=qaman>Qaman</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 3552<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/19/03 2:51 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Instant click items</span><hr size=1> Best instant click is probably the Amulet of Necropotence. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4380">Qaman</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
